title: To Holy Ground - Berserk Vol 17. [Part 3] - Vol. 19 [Part 1]
description:
Let's keep the Berserk ride going!
This video covers Berserk Deluxe Edition 6 & 7 - Vol. 17 [Part 3] & Vol. 18 [Part 1]. 
This includes the chapters:
"To Holy Ground 1-2" and "Kushan Scouts 1-2", "Tower of Shadow 1-2", "Children of Shadow", "Fierce Believer", "Bowels of the Holy Ground", "The Witch", "Spirit Road 1-2", and "Pillar of Flame" as well as "The Black Swordsman on Holy Ground".
